The solos are particularly syncopated, John likes to the flirt around the beat so I've tried to help you follow his timings. To properly read the timing, reference the beat of the measure that sits directly on top of the note being played. Be sure to check out the rhythm index to correctly decipher between a triplet and 16th note count.
